cc:Work.dc:title: Lauhging Man Logo from Ghost In The Shell - Stand Alone Complex
cc:Work.dc:description:
I (Weird Constructor) traced the SVG back in 2006 directly from the Anime. It was a long time online on one of a friends website. I decided to upload it to Github 2018.
The rights of the original logo and it's copyrights belong to the original creator and anime studio. However, there are lots of people who don't care....

g.aria-label: I thought what I'd do was, I'd pretend I was one of those deaf-mutes
